description	"New Republic Sapper

^2Weaponry:
- A-180 Blaster Pistol (2)
- 8 Trip Mines
- 2 Detonator Packs
- 3 Sonic Detonators
- 2 Frag Grenades
- 2 Thermal Detonator

^6Inventory:
- Medpac (25HP+)
- Portable Shield
- Portable Sentry Gun

^8Attributes:
- Blast Armour 
- Healing (3)
- Assemble (1)

A New Republic explosives specialists expert. He can lay traps to slow the advance of the Remnant. His armor is improved to better withstand kinetic and explosive force."